[SCOFFS]

15:39.564 --> 15:41.107
Whoa, hold up.

15:41.107 --> 15:43.735
Justice will be served

15:41.107 --> 15:43.735
in four and a half minutes,

15:43.735 --> 15:45.194
9 a.m. sharp.

15:45.194 --> 15:46.696
I look forward

15:45.194 --> 15:46.696
to sitting down

15:46.696 --> 15:48.406
with each and every

15:46.696 --> 15:48.406
one of you.

15:51.158 --> 15:53.994
Morning rush.

15:51.158 --> 15:53.994
So, that's your station.

15:53.994 --> 15:55.996
Temporarily. Of course.

15:55.996 --> 15:59.292
But check it out:

15:55.996 --> 15:59.292
center stage.

16:00.251 --> 16:01.335
What?

16:04.088 --> 16:06.716
That? It's garbagio,

16:06.716 --> 16:08.468
on its way

16:06.716 --> 16:08.468
to the dumpster, heh.

16:10.261 --> 16:13.848
I know that this place

16:10.261 --> 16:13.848
needs a little TLC.

16:13.848 --> 16:15.892
But this is just day one.

16:15.892 --> 16:18.060
Two weeks from now,

16:15.892 --> 16:18.060
you won't recognize it.

16:18.060 --> 16:19.646
Where's Ms. Wexler?

16:21.021 --> 16:22.523
You mean, my wife?

16:22.523 --> 16:25.568
That's right.

16:22.523 --> 16:25.568
Made an honest woman out of her.

16:25.568 --> 16:28.195
She's blazing her own trail

16:25.568 --> 16:28.195
and I couldn't be prouder.

16:28.195 --> 16:30.281
So it's just...?

16:30.281 --> 16:32.366
Me. Just me. For now.

16:32.366 --> 16:34.076
But think of it this way:

16:34.828 --> 16:36.370
half the work.

16:36.370 --> 16:41.334
[SIGHS]

16:36.370 --> 16:41.334
What happened to

16:36.370 --> 16:41.334
the old folks? Elder law?

16:41.334 --> 16:46.422
Uh, I expanded the mission, uh,

16:41.334 --> 16:46.422
to be more inclusive.

16:46.422 --> 16:48.382
Here at Saul Goodman

16:46.422 --> 16:48.382
and Associates,

16:48.382 --> 16:52.219
we welcome all ages,

16:48.382 --> 16:52.219
all creeds, all stripes.

16:52.219 --> 16:54.931
And who is

16:52.219 --> 16:54.931
this Saul Goodman?

16:56.056 --> 16:58.225
You?

16:56.056 --> 16:58.225
You got it!

16:58.225 --> 17:00.353
What Colonel Sanders is

16:58.225 --> 17:00.353
to chicken,

17:00.353 --> 17:03.105
Saul Goodman is to the law.

17:03.105 --> 17:04.858
Why me?

17:03.105 --> 17:04.858
Because I trust you.

17:04.858 --> 17:06.400
And...

17:06.400 --> 17:09.612
what happened last time,

17:06.400 --> 17:09.612
I-I wanna make it up to you.

17:09.612 --> 17:12.866
I will explain at the end

17:09.612 --> 17:12.866
of the day. Please...

17:12.866 --> 17:14.241
You're--

17:14.241 --> 17:16.452
You're just desperate

17:14.241 --> 17:16.452
and need a warm body.

17:16.452 --> 17:17.620
Good luck.

17:17.620 --> 17:19.998
Where are you going?

17:17.620 --> 17:19.998
Back to the MVD.

17:19.998 --> 17:22.041
I took half a personal day

17:19.998 --> 17:22.041
for this.

17:22.041 --> 17:24.377
What if I double your salary?

17:24.377 --> 17:26.045
My salary at the MVD

17:26.045 --> 17:28.130
or what you were paying me

17:26.045 --> 17:28.130
before?

17:29.507 --> 17:30.633
Whatever's less.

17:30.633 --> 17:32.176
[SCOFFS]

17:30.633 --> 17:32.176
No, whatever's more!

17:32.176 --> 17:34.929
"More" is the word

17:32.176 --> 17:34.929
I'm looking for.

17:34.929 --> 17:36.014
Did I mention...

17:37.807 --> 17:39.726
[EXHALES]

17:37.807 --> 17:39.726
...the signing bonus?

17:47.025 --> 17:48.985
I get a say

17:47.025 --> 17:48.985
in the decorating.

17:50.570 --> 17:52.363
Open for business!

17:52.363 --> 17:55.074
One at a time. Thank you.

17:52.363 --> 17:55.074
I'll be right out.

18:11.257 --> 18:13.133
Viola, hey, over here.

18:17.304 --> 18:19.682
Thanks for meeting me.

18:17.304 --> 18:19.682
VIOLA: Of course.

18:21.893 --> 18:23.436
I wanted to apologize.

18:25.730 --> 18:29.609
Leaving Schweikart, I'm sure

18:25.730 --> 18:29.609
it looked sudden, but...

18:30.777 --> 18:32.737
Sorry I left you in the lurch.

18:33.988 --> 18:37.366
You probably had

18:33.988 --> 18:37.366
to clean up Mesa Verde,

18:37.366 --> 18:39.827
everything

18:37.366 --> 18:39.827
that happened there.

18:39.827 --> 18:40.912
Kevin.

18:41.955 --> 18:43.039
Kevin.

18:44.707 --> 18:47.460
Anyway, I'm sure

18:44.707 --> 18:47.460
it's a lot.

18:47.460 --> 18:49.921
Actually, Mesa Verde

18:47.460 --> 18:49.921
calmed down.

18:49.921 --> 18:51.965
Rich moved me over

18:49.921 --> 18:51.965
to Sandpiper.

18:51.965 --> 18:55.927
Mm. Right.

18:51.965 --> 18:55.927
I think I heard that.

18:56.719 --> 18:57.845
How's it going?

18:57.845 --> 19:00.222
It's pretty interesting

18:57.845 --> 19:00.222
so far.

19:00.222 --> 19:02.767
It's a deep dive

19:00.222 --> 19:02.767
into class action.

19:02.767 --> 19:04.936
We have our first

19:02.767 --> 19:04.936
mediation session

19:04.936 --> 19:06.395
in a couple of weeks.

19:06.395 --> 19:08.606
Oh, already.

19:06.395 --> 19:08.606
Who'd you get?

19:08.606 --> 19:10.274
Hope it's not

19:08.606 --> 19:10.274
Roger Patch.

19:10.274 --> 19:12.234
Oh, God. Patch?

19:12.234 --> 19:14.070
With the vegan patties?

19:14.988 --> 19:16.363
What is in

19:14.988 --> 19:16.363
