19:16.363 --> 19:19.325
It's gotta be

19:16.363 --> 19:19.325
80 percent garlic.

19:19.325 --> 19:20.326
So healthy!

19:20.326 --> 19:21.786
[BOTH LAUGH]

19:23.245 --> 19:26.666
No, it's not--

19:23.245 --> 19:26.666
It's a new guy.

19:26.666 --> 19:27.834
A retired judge,

19:27.834 --> 19:31.004
who lives up in Santa Fe.

19:27.834 --> 19:31.004
Casimiro.

19:32.296 --> 19:34.715
He seems fine. Smells fine.

19:34.715 --> 19:36.968
[CHUCKLES]

19:34.715 --> 19:36.968
Well, then,

19:34.715 --> 19:36.968
you dodged a bullet.

19:38.385 --> 19:40.471
I'm glad you called.

19:40.471 --> 19:41.889
I've been wanting to tell you.

19:41.889 --> 19:45.810
Everyone was so shocked

19:41.889 --> 19:45.810
when you walked away.

19:45.810 --> 19:47.603
I mean...

19:47.603 --> 19:48.771
you were a partner.

19:48.771 --> 19:52.150
I'm sure it seemed very...

19:48.771 --> 19:52.150
weird.

19:52.150 --> 19:54.110
It did at first.

19:52.150 --> 19:54.110
But I get it now.

19:54.110 --> 19:56.403
What you're doing

19:54.110 --> 19:56.403
to help the little guy...

19:57.530 --> 19:59.448
it's incredible.

19:59.448 --> 20:01.325
I'm just getting started.

20:01.325 --> 20:04.411
I really admire you, Kim.

20:04.411 --> 20:06.664
Changing direction

20:04.411 --> 20:06.664
like that.

20:06.664 --> 20:10.292
Sometimes I question

20:06.664 --> 20:10.292
all of it, but...

20:12.837 --> 20:14.964
You make me feel better

20:12.837 --> 20:14.964
about the law.

20:17.008 --> 20:18.509
[CHUCKLES]

20:29.020 --> 20:30.521
JIMMY:

20:29.020 --> 20:30.521
Hit and run, 15 minutes.

20:30.521 --> 20:34.316
Shoplifting?

20:30.521 --> 20:34.316
I can knock that out in 10.

20:34.316 --> 20:35.317
Yeah, 10.

20:35.317 --> 20:36.443
Hey...

20:36.443 --> 20:38.278
This ain't fine dining,

20:36.443 --> 20:38.278
okay?

20:38.278 --> 20:40.823
Our business model

20:38.278 --> 20:40.823
is turning tables.

20:40.823 --> 20:42.950
So Francesca, I'm here.

20:42.950 --> 20:45.369
Remind me again

20:42.950 --> 20:45.369
why I'm making a house call?

20:46.829 --> 20:49.082
Sounds like money.

20:46.829 --> 20:49.082
Okay. Great.

20:49.082 --> 20:51.250
Great work.

20:49.082 --> 20:51.250
[BLUETOOTH BEEPS OFF]

20:53.460 --> 20:54.712
Mr. Ward?

20:59.050 --> 21:00.134
Hi.

21:06.306 --> 21:07.934
[CLEARS THROAT]

21:07.934 --> 21:09.143
I'm an attorney.

21:09.143 --> 21:11.520
I have an appointment

21:09.143 --> 21:11.520
